<H1>3 AST Support Programs</A></H1><hr>
<H2>3.1 Pronto Pro</A>!<BR></H2>
Subscription to AST's Pronto Pro! is mandatory for
al Authorized Service Centres.  Pronto Pro! a CD Rom containing
all configuration, set up and troubleshooting information on current
AST products.  It is easy and fast to use .  It also contains
model by model parts lists.  Any part of the reference material
can be output to hard copy.<BR>
<P>
Pronto Pro requires a  386 or higher with 4mb RAM,
Windows 3.1 or higher and a VGA display.  It will be distributed
bi-monthly to all ASC's who take out a subscription ( see Attachment
2).
